    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796350/extras/da0b8d6df1af13d6a4773a9bf2f081b2.avif?t=1647983794\" width=566 height=326 /></span><br>Compete in a <u>super-dynamic hybrid</u> of arcade soccer and first person shooter!<br>Be active, attack, win. In the <u>new sports game</u>!<br>Hit the field by yourself or with friends in 1vs1, 2vs2 and 3vs3.<br>Use many <strong>Special Perks</strong> combinations to make the match even more <strong>CRAZY</strong>.<br><u>Create your dream team</u> and become the best!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796350/extras/f10e3ab420dc74dae7e7287b307a5b48.poster.avif?t=1647983794\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796350/extras/f10e3ab420dc74dae7e7287b307a5b48.webm?t=1647983794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1796350/extras/f10e3ab420dc74dae7e7287b307a5b48.mp4?t=1647983794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As in classic soccer, you need to score more goals than your opponent during the match.<br>Use a machine gun, rocket launcher or grenade launcher, depending on the situation.<br><strong>PERK SYSTEM</strong><br>You can choose 3 perks before the start of the match.<br>Perks can be selected manually or randomly.<br>Perks are divided into three types:<br>- Weapon perks.<br>- Map perks.<br>- Ball perks.<br>For example, you can turn on gravity, teleporters and moving columns.<br>Each combination of perks creates a unique gaming experience.<br>Find your favorite combination of perks.",
